      <p begin="01:10:36.145" end="01:10:38.175" region="top">1985 American Psychological Association</p>
      <p begin="01:10:38.175" end="01:10:40.004" region="top"> toont verbnand aan <br/>tussen Tv geweld en echt geweld</p>
